Package: seurathelpeR
Type: Package
Title: Helper Functions For Seurat V3
Version: 0.0.0.9000
Author: Kin Lau
Maintainer: Kin Lau <kin.lau@vai.org>
Description: This package contains helper functions for working with Seurat v3 objects. The goal 
    is to provide convenience functions to facilitate a closer exqmination of the various aspects 
    of a single-cell project analyzed using Seurat v3.
